{"type": "article", "id": 11846, "title": "摇椅秋千", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-09T11:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115243o6eMfxEOCaJitD27.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师 Clara Rivière 和 Tobias Nickerl 把摇椅和秋千合二为一，设计了一个摇摆秋千 “Rocking Swing”，你可以摇，可以荡秋千，也可以边摇边荡秋千。他们说希望让使用者找到儿时玩儿秋千的乐趣和老年人坐摇椅的感觉，听起来有点儿分裂，但设计师表示希望通过这件作品找到跨代际的交流和乐趣。不管怎样，秋千摇椅简洁的外观，大胆的配色和可爱的设计理念，让人看见就莫名开心了许多呢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135844dI5fGyHlTYowP73a.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"924\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.12958435\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135845nEipGQ70HdOwqUeS.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1048\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.31\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135846o6w7PMRDSFCtHNXg.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1198\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.4975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135846Kv2aSsq6ZitzfEcw.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}